23
00:01:30,790 --> 00:01:34,690
We separated out even material considerations, considered

24
00:01:34,690 --> 00:01:40,540
the patronage, in order to think of architecture as constructing

25
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:43,800
its own world within a world.

26
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:50,080
And the world that it constructs cannot be reduced to mere purpose.

27
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:53,230
Now, this part of our model of the architectural imagination

28
00:01:53,230 --> 00:01:57,130
