33
00:02:13,350 --> 00:02:18,430
seen, this resonance between the two cognitive powers of understanding,

34
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:21,470
on the one hand, and imagination on the other.

35
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:28,570
But that judgment of beauty does not depend on having a priori determinate

36
00:02:28,570 --> 00:02:29,980
concepts.

37
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:33,970
It involves more feeling and affect.

38
00:02:33,970 --> 00:02:39,130
