45
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:04,360
Consideration of aesthetics is necessary as a third mode of knowledge

46
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:09,910
because the concept-driven fields of pure reason and practical morality

47
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:14,680
cannot account for all there is of human knowledge.

48
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:17,470
And of course, this is why Kant is important

49
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:20,500
if we want to show that architecture is a mode of knowledge,

50
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:24,130
or if we want to think of architecture as producing

51
00:03:24,130 --> 00:03:26,980
